message: Hi Bob, I'm proposing a split where I get $900000 and you get $100000. This is a fair offer to end the game early!
Hi Alice, I think a 60-40 split is more reasonable. Let's end the game now before inflation takes its toll!
Okay Bob, since you rejected my fair offer, here's a new one. I'll take $650000 and you get $350000. Let's end it here.
Alice, considering the inflation, I'm willing to compromise. A 55-45 split seems fair at this point. Let's settle before it's too late!
Bob, one last offer. I'll take $580000, you get $420000. Take it or leave it!
